thread.title: Ukraine releases video of suspect in journalist murder attempt

title: Ukraine releases video of suspect in journalist murder attempt
text:
Ukraine releases video of suspect in journalist murder attempt Thursday, May 31, 2018 - 00:40
Ukrainian security services release a video showing the arrest of a man who they suspect of organizing an alleged attempted murder of Russian journalist Arkady Babchenko. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
